            <h1 class="section-title">Membership</h1>
            <p>Membership of the Association is open to all individuals and institutions interested in furthering its aims.​</p>
            <p>Full membership benefits include the annual journal, Scottish Archives, the bi-annual newsletter, Retour, reduced rates at the annual conference and news about other relevant events including Association visits to archives and repositories.</p>
            <p>Individual members in the UK and abroad can opt for full membership or reduced membership (all publications except the journal). A student membership is also available.</p>
            <p>To join the Association, please print, complete and return the <a href="/documents/sra-membership-form-2023.pdf" target="_blank">membership form</a> with the appropriate payment. Alternatively, you can use our <a href="https://membershipsra.wordpress.com/" target="_blank">online membership form</a>. If you have any queries, please email: <a href="mailto:sra-membership@abbotshall.net">sra-membership@abbotshall.net</a>.</p>
